<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الإِقْرَارِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> يَصِحُّ مِنْ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> مُكَلَّفٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> مُخْتَارٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- بِلَفْظٍ، أَوْ كِتَابَةٍ، أَوْ إِشَارَةِ أَخْرَسَ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- لَا عَلَى الغَيْرِ،<span class="c5"> إِلَّا مِنْ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- وَكِيلٍ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَوَلِيٍّ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>- وَوَارِثٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ مِنْ مَرِيضٍ مَرَضَ المَوْتِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- لَا بِمَالٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> لِوَارِثٍ إِلَّا بِبَيِّنَةٍ أَوْ إِجَازَةٍ، وَلَوْ صَارَ عِنْدَ المَوْتِ أَجْنَبِيًّا.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- وَيَصِحُّ لِأَجْنَبِيٍّ، وَلَوْ صَارَ عِنْدَ المَوْتِ وَارِثاً.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (بمال) سقطت من (أ) و (ج).</p> </div>